Jump around!</i>

754
00:38:02,544 --> 00:38:03,550
<i>Jump around!</i>

755
00:38:04,527 --> 00:38:06,745
<i>Jump up, jump up,
and get down!</i>

756
00:38:06,799 --> 00:38:10,995
<i>Jump, jump, jump!
Everybody, jump, jump!</i>

757
00:38:11,566 --> 00:38:12,432
Come on, ladies,

758
00:38:12,949 --> 00:38:14,058
don't be shy.

