00:38:15,905 --> 00:38:17,065
You want more champagne?

760
00:38:17,222 --> 00:38:19,716
I'm on it... room service,
whatever you want.

761
00:38:19,781 --> 00:38:20,994
Chicken fingers,

762
00:38:21,061 --> 00:38:22,725
cake, fine cheeses.

763
00:38:22,879 --> 00:38:23,936
Just name it,

764
00:38:23,962 --> 00:38:26,529
'cause you are very special ladies...

765
00:38:26,886 --> 00:38:28,738
and I'm on someone else's tab.

